    <item>
      <title>Yelp 在搜索领域反垄断裁决出炉后起诉谷歌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/yelp-sues-google-in-wake-of-landmark-antitrust-ruling-on-search</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在线评论网站 Yelp Inc. 提起诉讼，指控谷歌在本地搜索领域拥有非法垄断权，这表明在美国政府对谷歌取得具有里程碑意义的反垄断胜利之后，这家搜索巨头可能将面临法律难题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/yelp-sues-google-in-wake-of-landmark-antitrust-ruling-on-search</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 00:28:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
